      "rebuttal_id": "rJlvwS37sS",
      "sentence_index": 1,
      "text": "However, to state the result of Theorem 4.3, $k$ should be bigger than $M c_\\eta$ from the dentition of $\\tilde{\\rho}_k^M$, as shown under the equation (4).",
      "suffix": "",
      "coarse": "nonarg",
